title: 10/04/21 DPS Hour 2

description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan examines some of the Patriots' late-game strategy in their loss to Tampa Bay and he has some hindsight pointers for New England. Also, there were plenty of eyebrow-raising moments from Saturday's college football scene that caught Dan's attention.
